<view class="page results-page"><view class="search-header-wrap"><view class="search-input-box"><view class="search-glass-icon"></view><input class="header-search-input" placeholder="输入关键词搜索承运商" placeholder-style="color:#94a3b8" bindconfirm="{{a}}" value="{{b}}" bindinput="{{c}}"/></view><button class="primary-btn search-confirm-btn" bindtap="{{d}}">搜索</button></view><view class="route-details-banner"><view wx:if="{{e}}" class="route-text-line"><text class="route-point">按承运商关键词查询</text></view><view wx:else class="route-text-line"><text class="route-point">{{f}}</text><text class="route-connector-arrow">⇄</text><text class="route-point">{{g}}</text></view></view><view class="sub-filter-pills-row"><view class="{{['sub-filter-pill', h && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{i}}"><text class="sub-filter-check"></text><text>大板运输</text></view><view class="{{['sub-filter-pill', j && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{k}}"><text class="sub-filter-check"></text><text>全程小板</text></view><view class="{{['sub-filter-pill', l && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{m}}"><text class="sub-filter-check"></text><text>代驾</text></view></view><view wx:if="{{n}}" class="carrier-count-summary"> 已筛选出 {{o}} 家{{p}}</view><view wx:if="{{q}}" class="empty-results-v2"><view class="empty-content"><text class="empty-title">暂无匹配的承运商</text><text class="empty-action-desc">建议更换起始城市、目的地或关键词后重新查询。</text></view></view><block wx:elif="{{r}}"><view wx:for="{{s}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="g" class="section carrier-card-v2"><view class="carrier-card-header"><view class="carrier-title-block"><view class="carrier-name-title-row"><text class="carrier-company-name">{{item.a}}</text><view class="carrier-badges-row"><image class="carrier-verify-icon" src="{{t}}" mode="aspectFit"/><view class="carrier-service-badge"><image class="carrier-badge-icon" src="{{v}}" mode="aspectFit"/><text class="carrier-badge-text">限时达</text></view><view class="carrier-service-badge"><image class="carrier-badge-icon" src="{{w}}" mode="aspectFit"/><text class="carrier-badge-text">{{item.b}}</text></view></view></view><view class="carrier-intro-link" bindtap="{{item.c}}"><text class="carrier-intro-icon">介</text><text class="carrier-intro-text">承运商介绍</text><text class="carrier-intro-arrow">›</text></view></view></view><view class="carrier-services-block"><view wx:for="{{item.d}}" wx:for-item="srv" wx:key="g" class="service-price-row"><text class="service-name-label">{{srv.a}}</text><view class="service-meta-right"><text wx:if="{{srv.b}}" class="service-time-lbl">约最快 {{srv.c}} 送达</text><text wx:if="{{srv.d}}" class="{{['service-price-val', srv.f && 'highlight']}}">{{srv.e}}</text></view></view></view><view class="carrier-actions-block"><button class="secondary-btn contact-action-btn" bindtap="{{item.e}}">电话联系</button><button class="primary-btn create-order-action-btn" bindtap="{{item.f}}"> 发起订单 </button></view></view></block><view wx:if="{{x}}" class="loading-box"><dealer-icon wx:if="{{y}}" class="loading-spinner" u-i="06e19cf0-0" bind:__l="__l" u-p="{{y}}"/><text class="loading-text">正在全网帮您寻找承运商...</text></view><view wx:if="{{z}}" class="intro-panel-mask" bindtap="{{H}}"><view class="intro-panel" catchtap="{{G}}"><view class="intro-panel-handle"></view><view class="intro-panel-header"><text class="intro-panel-title">{{A}}</text><text class="intro-panel-close" bindtap="{{B}}">×</text></view><scroll-view scroll-y class="intro-panel-content"><view wx:if="{{C}}" class="intro-loading">加载中...</view><block wx:else><view class="intro-block"><text class="intro-block-title">介绍说明</text><text class="intro-panel-text">{{D}}</text></view><view class="intro-block"><text class="intro-block-title">联系地址</text><view wx:if="{{E}}" class="intro-empty-address"> 该承运商暂未公开联系地址 </view><view wx:for="{{F}}" wx:for-item="address" wx:key="h" class="intro-address-card"><view class="intro-address-head"><text class="intro-address-name">{{address.a}}</text><text class="intro-address-city">{{address.b}}</text></view><text class="intro-address-detail">{{address.c}}</text><text class="intro-address-phone">电话：{{address.d}}</text><view class="intro-address-actions"><button class="intro-address-btn" bindtap="{{address.e}}"> 地图查看 </button><button class="intro-address-btn" bindtap="{{address.f}}">复制地址</button><button class="intro-address-btn primary" bindtap="{{address.g}}"> 拨打电话 </button></view></view></view></block></scroll-view></view></view></view>